        <item>
            <title>加拿大不满美国关税战，网民提议 Pornhub 封锁美国作「报复」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/17/canada-standup-comedian-suggest-ban-us-access-to-pornhub/movie-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=canada-standup-comedian-suggest-ban-us-access-to-pornhub</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/17/canada-standup-comedian-suggest-ban-us-access-to-pornhub/movie-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 07:20:10 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影视娱乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[pornhub]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[加拿大]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[美国]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1297884</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>美国总统特朗普对加拿大实施关税，并多次暗示加拿大可成为美国第 51 州，激起加国民众不满。近日一名加拿大栋笃笑演员 Matthew Puzhitsky 在社交平台 Instagram 发布短片，提议禁止美国用户访问加拿大成人网站 Pornhub，作为对美关税战的反制手段。此建议迅速引起热议，甚至有民众发起请愿支持。Pornhub 母公司 Aylo 总部位于加拿大满地可，其美国流量占比近 40%，每月浏览量逾 300 万次。</p><blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DHEco2WPsuL/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14"><div style="padding: 16px;"><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display: block; height: 50px; margin: 0 auto 12px; width: 50px;"></div><div style="padding-top: 8px;"><div style="color: #3897f0; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 550; line-height: 18px;">在 Instagram 查看这则贴文</div></div><div style="padding: 12.5% 0;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; margin-bottom: 14px; align-items: center;"><div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(0px) translateY(7px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; height: 12.5px; transform: rotate(-45deg) translateX(3px) translateY(1px); width: 12.5px; flex-grow: 0; margin-right: 14px; margin-left: 2px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(9px) translateY(-18px);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: 8px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 20px; width: 20px;"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: auto;"><div style="width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);"></div></div></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 224px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 144px;"></div></div><p style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; padding: 8px 0 7px; text-align: center; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;"><a style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DHEco2WPsuL/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Matthew Puzhitsky（@mattpuzhitsky）分享的贴文</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//www.instagram.com/embed.js"></script></p><h2>加拿大反制关税战的「核武」提案</h2><p>Puzhitsky 在短片中一人分饰两角，幽默表示若加拿大能禁止美国用户使用 Pornhub，「贸易战将不复存在」。他在接受《纽约邮报》访问时称，此举是加拿大的「核武器」。据报导，Pornhub 于 2007 年成立，是全球三大成人网站之一，对美国用户尤具吸引力。有分析指，美国用户若失去访问权，恐对其日常生活及心理造成显著影响。</p><p>此建议启发部分加拿大人发起请愿，呼吁政府立法限制 Pornhub 在美国的服务。截至 2025 年 3 月 16 日，请愿已获 590 个签名。请愿书指，关税争端已影响经济多个层面，禁用 Pornhub 可向美国发出强烈讯号，促其重新考虑政策。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031713527-694x514.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="514" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031713527-694x514.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031713527.jpg 1012w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.change.org/p/urge-canadian-authorities-to-block-pornhub-access-from-the-usa-during-tariff-dispute">Change.org</a></p><p>美国民众则反应不一，据《纽约邮报》指，有人扬言如果加拿大人剥夺美国人上 Pornhub 的权利，他将会移民，亦有人质疑加拿大是否真会采取如此激烈行动。Pornhub 禁令提案虽源于玩笑，却意外成为美加关税战的焦点话题。随着请愿声势渐长及贸易谈判持续，此事或许会迫使双方重新评估立场。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DHEco2WPsuL/">mattpuzhitsky@Instagram</a>、<a href="https://nypost.com/2025/03/15/world-news/canada-has-nuclear-weapon-in-trade-war-ban-pornhub-in-us/">New York Post</a>、<a href="https://www.livemint.com/news/world/blocking-pornhub-in-the-us-canada-s-ultimate-trade-war-power-move-11742136382393.html">mint</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
